DefaultEvent.Description:
$Isery -> イザリー$Isery snatches the notes from your hands, and starts flicking through the pages. "I'll have a reward sent to your ship." They look up and smile at you vaguely, eyes glazed as a honey-seeker's. "Oh, my dear, what a treasure you are."

 You summon an answering smile, and slip away the moment they are distracted.

ChildBranches.Name: A well-earned reward
ChildBranches.Description: $Alarming Scholar -> 不安を催させる学者$You hand over the Alarming Scholar's notes.

Description: $Isery -> イザリー$"Don't keep me waiting!" Isery pouts prettily, and rustles their silks. "Do you have a little present for me?"
Name: A Smuggler's Reward
